locality: Distr. Lobatera; La Cazadora, dry evergreen scrub or low forest, to 10 m tall. Myrtac., Malpighia., & Verben., common, very few terrestrial ferns,almost no vascular epiphytes (few Bromeliads). Disturbed by cattle.
